sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant App as [Android App]
  participant MTX as [MediaMTX]
  participant Storage as [Raw Storage]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant Redis as [Redis]
  participant DB as [DB]
  participant Queue as [Finalize Queue]
  participant Worker as [Finalize Worker]

  Note over App,MTX: AppмқҖ мқҙлҜё м—ҙлҰ° RTMP publisher socketмқ„ мң м§Җн•ңлӢӨ.
  Note over MTX,Backend: м „м ң<br/>.mermaid/RTMP/3.rtmp-publish.mmd лӢЁкі„м—җм„ң stream-ready hookмқҙ мІҳлҰ¬лҗҳм–ҙ<br/>live cacheмҷҖ active setмқҙ л“ұлЎқлҗң мғҒнғңлӢӨ.<br/><br/>recording-segment-create hookлҸ„ мқҙлҜё мІҳлҰ¬лҗҳм–ҙ<br/>recording_segments rowк°Җ WRITING мғҒнғңлЎң мғқм„ұлҗҳм–ҙ мһҲкі <br/>raw_pathлҠ” MediaMTXк°Җ м—ҙм–ҙ л‘” segment_pathмҷҖ к°ҷлӢӨ.

  loop while RTMP socket is open
    App->>MTX: RTMP media chunks
    Note over App,MTX: video<br/>H.264/H.265 sequence header<br/>encoded video samples<br/><br/>audio<br/>AAC sequence header<br/>encoded audio samples<br/><br/>timestamp<br/>App encoder PTS кё°мӨҖ

    MTX-->>App: RTMP control messages
    Note over MTX,App: acknowledgement<br/>window acknowledgement<br/>ping/pong л“ұ connection мң м§Җмҡ© control message

    MTX->>Storage: fMP4 part append/write
    Note over MTX,Storage: recordPath<br/>/data/raw/live/{repositoryName}/{recordingSessionId}/{timestamp}<br/><br/>recordFormat<br/>fmp4<br/><br/>recordPartDuration<br/>1s<br/><br/>recordSegmentDuration<br/>2h

    Note over MTX,Backend: мқҙ кө¬к°„м—җм„ңлҠ” backend per-frame нҳём¶ңмқҙ м—ҶлӢӨ.<br/>ticket мһ¬кІҖмҰқлҸ„ мҲҳн–үн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
  end

  alt normal stop
    App->>Backend: POST /api/v1/recordings/{recordingSessionId}/close-intent
    Note over App,Backend: body.reason=NORMAL_DISCONNECT<br/>App JWT н•„мҡ”<br/>session owner + STREAMING мғҒнғңл§Ң н—Ҳмҡ©
    Note over App,Backend: error cases<br/>401 invalid App JWT<br/>400 invalid params/body<br/>404 session missing<br/>403 non-owner<br/>409 session not STREAMING
    Backend->>DB: close intent record
    Note over Backend,DB: table: recording_sessions<br/>target row: id = recordingSessionId<br/>updated fields: end_reason=NORMAL_DISCONNECT<br/>status/closed_at/RedisлҠ” ліҖкІҪн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
    Backend-->>App: 200 OK

    App->>MTX: RTMP socket close
    Note over App,MTX: мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗк°Җ мў…лЈҢ лІ„нҠјмқ„ лҲ„лҘҙл©ҙ AppмқҖ close-intent кё°лЎқ нӣ„<br/>publisher socketмқ„ м •мғҒ closeн•ңлӢӨ.<br/>MediaMTXлҠ” publisher м—°кІ° мў…лЈҢлҘј к°җм§Җн•ңлӢӨ.
  else app crash or network failure
    Note over App,MTX: App crash, process kill, radio/network loss л“ұмңјлЎң<br/>close-intent м—Ҷмқҙ MediaMTXк°Җ TCP close/reset/timeoutмқ„ к°җм§Җн•ңлӢӨ.
  end

  Note over MTX,Backend: MediaMTX flush timingм—җ л”°лқј stream-not-readyмҷҖ segment-completeмқҳ лҸ„м°© мҲңм„ңлҠ” ліҙмһҘн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.<br/>stream-not-readyлҠ” RecordingSessionл§Ң лӢ«кі ,<br/>segment-completeлҠ” RecordingSegmentл§Ң WRITE_DONEмңјлЎң м „нҷҳн•ң л’Ө finalize enqueueлҘј мӢңлҸ„н•ңлӢӨ.

  alt stream-not-ready hook first
    MTX->>Backend: stream-not-ready hook
    Note over MTX,Backend: publisher connection мў…лЈҢ event<br/>path=live/{repositoryName}/{recordingSessionId}

    Backend->>DB: RecordingSession CLOSED update
    Note over Backend,DB: table: recording_sessions<br/>target row: id = recordingSessionId<br/>required status: STREAMING<br/>updated fields: status=CLOSED, closed_at, end_reason<br/>close-intentк°Җ мһҲмңјл©ҙ NORMAL_DISCONNECT ліҙмЎҙ<br/>м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ UNEXPECTED_DISCONNECT кё°лЎқ<br/><br/>no-op cases<br/>recordingSessionId м¶”м¶ң мӢӨнҢЁ<br/>session row м—ҶмқҢ<br/>statusк°Җ STREAMINGмқҙ м•„лӢҳ

    Backend->>Redis: live pointer cleanup
    Note over Backend,Redis: delete key: stream:recording:{recordingSessionId}<br/>remove member from set: stream:active:sessions

    Backend->>Backend: tryEnqueueFinalize(recordingSessionId)
    Backend->>DB: finalize readiness check
    Note over Backend,DB: required state<br/>RecordingSession.status = CLOSED<br/>RecordingSegment.status = WRITE_DONE

    Backend->>Backend: no-op
    Note over Backend: segment-completeк°Җ м•„м§Ғ мҳӨм§Җ м•Ҡм•ҳмңјлҜҖлЎң enqueueн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.

    MTX->>Storage: last fMP4 segment close and flush
    MTX->>Backend: recording-segment-complete hook
    Note over MTX,Backend: raw segment file write мҷ„лЈҢ event<br/>path=live/{repositoryName}/{recordingSessionId}<br/>segment_path={completed_segment_path}

    Backend->>DB: RecordingSegment WRITE_DONE update
    Note over Backend,DB: table: recording_segments<br/>target row: recording_session_id = recordingSessionId<br/>required status: WRITING<br/>required raw_path: completed_segment_path<br/>updated fields: status=WRITE_DONE, completed_at<br/>RecordingSessionмқҖ ліҖкІҪн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.<br/><br/>no-op cases<br/>recordingSessionId м¶”м¶ң мӢӨнҢЁ<br/>segment row м—ҶмқҢ<br/>raw_path mismatch<br/>statusк°Җ WRITINGмқҙ м•„лӢҳ

    Backend->>Backend: tryEnqueueFinalize(recordingSessionId)
    Backend->>DB: finalize readiness check
    Backend->>Queue: recording-finalize enqueue
    Note over Backend,Queue: мЎ°кұҙ м¶©мЎұ мӢң enqueue<br/>session is CLOSED + single segment is WRITE_DONE<br/>jobId = finalize-{recordingSessionId}<br/>payload includes videoId=randomUUID

  else recording-segment-complete hook first
    MTX->>Storage: last fMP4 segment close and flush
    MTX->>Backend: recording-segment-complete hook
    Backend->>DB: RecordingSegment WRITE_DONE update
    Backend->>Backend: tryEnqueueFinalize(recordingSessionId)
    Backend->>DB: RecordingSession мғҒнғң мЎ°нҡҢ<br/>м•„м§Ғ CLOSEDк°Җ м•„лӢҳ
    Backend->>Backend: no-op

    MTX->>Backend: stream-not-ready hook
    Note over MTX,Backend: path=live/{repositoryName}/{recordingSessionId}
    Backend->>DB: RecordingSession CLOSED update
    Backend->>Redis: live pointer cleanup
    Backend->>Backend: tryEnqueueFinalize(recordingSessionId)
    Backend->>DB: finalize readiness check
    Backend->>Queue: recording-finalize enqueue
    Note over Backend,Queue: jobId = finalize-{recordingSessionId}<br/>мӨ‘ліө enqueueлҠ” BullMQ jobIdлЎң dedupe
  end

  Queue->>Worker: finalize job
  Worker->>DB: RecordingSession metadata мЎ°нҡҢ
  Note over Worker,DB: target row: id = recordingSessionId<br/>status мһ¬кІҖмҰқмқҖ н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.<br/>finalize enqueueк°Җ мқҙлҜё CLOSED + WRITE_DONE readinessлҘј ліҙмһҘн•ңлӢӨ.

  Worker->>DB: RecordingSegment мЎ°нҡҢ
  Note over Worker,DB: target row<br/>recording_session_id = recordingSessionId<br/>segment statusлҠ” лі„лҸ„ л¶„кё° кІҖмҰқн•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡкі  atomic claim мЎ°кұҙмңјлЎң нҢҗлӢЁн•ңлӢӨ.

  alt segment missing
    Worker->>Worker: no-op
    Note over Worker: лҢҖмғҒ segmentк°Җ м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ<br/>нҳ„мһ¬ jobмқҖ мў…лЈҢн•ңлӢӨ.
  else segment found
    Worker->>DB: RecordingSegment atomic claim
    Note over Worker,DB: updateMany where id = segment.id and status = WRITE_DONE

    alt atomic claim missed
      Worker->>Worker: no-op
      Note over Worker: segmentк°Җ WRITE_DONEмқҙ м•„лӢҲкұ°лӮҳ<br/>лӢӨлҘё workerк°Җ лЁјм Җ claimн•ң кІғмңјлЎң ліҙкі <br/>нҳ„мһ¬ job attemptлҠ” мў…лЈҢн•ңлӢӨ.
    else atomic claim success
      Worker->>DB: WRITE_DONE -> PROCESSING
      Note over Worker,DB: claim count = 1мқё workerл§Ң processing м§„н–ү

      Worker->>DB: Video row upsert
      Note over Worker,DB: recording_session_id unique<br/>status = PROCESSING<br/>processingStartedAt кё°лЎқ<br/>repository detailм—җм„ң processing itemмңјлЎң л…ём¶ң

      Worker->>Worker: process recording finalize
      Note over Worker: task progressлҠ” BullMQ job.progressм—җ м ҖмһҘн•ңлӢӨ.<br/>shape: current_step, total_steps, task, label<br/><br/>1/7 initialize_video<br/>2/7 stabilize_raw<br/>3/7 probe_metadata<br/>4/7 prepare_outputs<br/>5/7 encode_assets<br/>6/7 verify_artifact<br/>7/7 persist_video<br/><br/>мғҒм„ё processing мғҒнғңлҠ” .mermaid/RTMP/5.video-processing.mmd м°ёкі 

      alt processing success
        Worker->>DB: finalize transaction
        Note over Worker,DB: same videos row upsert<br/>status = COMPLETED<br/>technical metadata, output paths, size, sha256 м ҖмһҘ<br/><br/>video_semantic_metadata row upsert<br/>status = PENDING<br/>semantic metadata к°’мқҖ м•„м§Ғ мғқм„ұн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠмқҢ<br/><br/>recording_segments row к°ұмӢ <br/>status = COMPLETED<br/><br/>repository row lock нӣ„ contributors refresh
        Worker->>Storage: optional raw cleanup
        Note over Worker,Storage: DELETE_RAW_AFTER_PROCESSING=trueмқҙл©ҙ<br/>raw segment file мӮӯм ң
      else processing failure and attempts remain
        Worker->>DB: PROCESSING -> WRITE_DONE
        Note over Worker,DB: retry м „м—җ segment мғҒнғңлҘј лҗҳлҸҢлҰ°лӢӨ.<br/>Video rowлҠ” к°ҷмқҖ recording_session_idлЎң PROCESSING мһ¬мӮ¬мҡ©<br/>лӢӨмқҢ attemptлҸ„ WRITE_DONE -> PROCESSING atomic claimл¶Җн„° лӢӨмӢң мӢңмһ‘н•ңлӢӨ.
        Worker->>Queue: retry scheduled
        Note over Worker,Queue: attempts = 3<br/>backoff = exponential<br/>initial delay = 5000ms
      else final processing failure
        Worker->>Worker: failed event
        Note over Worker: attemptsMade >= attempts мқј л•Ңл§Ң<br/>мӢӨнҢЁ мғҒнғңлҘј DBм—җ кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ.
        Worker->>DB: mark finalize failed transaction
        Note over Worker,DB: recording_segments row к°ұмӢ <br/>status = FAILED<br/><br/>same videos row upsert<br/>status = FAILED<br/>error_message = worker error
      end
    end
  end

%% м°ёкі :
%% мқҙ л¬ём„ңлҠ” live cache м ҖмһҘ мқҙнӣ„ мӢӨм ң RTMP media м „мҶЎ,
%% publisher socket мў…лЈҢ, stream-not-ready/segment-complete hook, finalize enqueueк№Ңм§Җ лӢӨлЈ¬лӢӨ.
%% App ліҖкІҪ н•„мҡ”:
%% Appмқҳ stop лІ„нҠјмқҖ legacy Stop APIлҘј нҳём¶ңн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
%% Appмқҳ stop лІ„нҠјмқҖ RTMP publisher connectionмқ„ л°”лЎң лӢ«кё° м „м—җ
%% POST /api/v1/recordings/{recordingSessionId}/close-intent лҘј нҳём¶ңн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.
%% close-intent bodyлҠ” { "reason": "NORMAL_DISCONNECT" } л§Ң ліҙлӮёлӢӨ.
%% close-intent 200 OK мқҙнӣ„ RTMP publisher connectionмқ„ м •мғҒ closeн•ңлӢӨ.
%% close-intent нҳём¶ң мӢӨнҢЁ лҳҗлҠ” app crash/network failureлЎң close-intentк°Җ лҲ„лқҪлҗҳл©ҙ
%% backendлҠ” stream-not-ready/reconcile мӢң UNEXPECTED_DISCONNECTлЎң кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ.
%% stream-not-ready hook payloadл§ҢмңјлЎң м •мғҒ closeмҷҖ crash/reset/timeoutмқ„ м •нҷ•нһҲ кө¬л¶„н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
%% close-intentк°Җ лЁјм Җ лҸ„м°©н•ң кІҪмҡ° stream-not-readyлҠ” NORMAL_DISCONNECTлҘј ліҙмЎҙн•ңлӢӨ.
%% close-intent м—Ҷмқҙ stream-not-readyк°Җ лҸ„м°©н•ҳкұ°лӮҳ MediaMTX active path missingмқ„ reconcileмқҙ к°җм§Җн•ҳл©ҙ UNEXPECTED_DISCONNECTлЎң кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ.
%% нҳ„мһ¬ кө¬мЎ°м—җм„ңлҠ” Appмқҙ лӢЁмқј recording sessionмқ„ м§§кІҢ мң м§Җн•ҳлҠ” м „м ңмқҙлҜҖлЎң
%% м •мғҒ нқҗлҰ„мқҳ segment rolloverлҠ” лі„лҸ„лЎң лӢӨлЈЁм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
%% finalize job мӨ‘ліө enqueueлҠ” jobId=finalize-{recordingSessionId}лЎң dedupeлҗңлӢӨ.
%% workerлҠ” session statusмҷҖ existing VideoлҘј мӮ¬м „ мһ¬кІҖмҰқн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
%% мІҳлҰ¬ к¶Ңн•ңмқҖ RecordingSegment WRITE_DONE -> PROCESSING atomic claimмңјлЎң ліҙмһҘн•ңлӢӨ.
%% м„ұкіө мӢң videos rowлҠ” recording_session_id unique key кё°мӨҖ upsertн•ңлӢӨ. мқҙлҠ” нҳ„мһ¬ мҪ”л“ң кё°мӨҖ мқҳлҸ„лҗң лҸҷмһ‘мқҙлӢӨ.
%% semantic metadataлҠ” video_semantic_metadata лі„лҸ„ tableм—җм„ң status/dataлҘј кҙҖлҰ¬н•ңлӢӨ.
%% WRITE_DONE segmentлҘј reconcileм—җм„ң лӢӨмӢң м°ҫм•„ enqueueн•ҳлҠ” ліҙм • loopлҠ” л‘җм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
%% retry к°ҖлҠҘн•ң worker мӢӨнҢЁм—җм„ңлҠ” PROCESSINGмқ„ WRITE_DONEмңјлЎң лҗҳлҸҢлҰ° л’Ө BullMQ retryм—җ л§ЎкёҙлӢӨ.
%% recording-finalize queue option: attempts=3, exponential backoff delay=5000ms, removeOnComplete=1000, removeOnFail=2000.
%% segment-complete hook лҲ„лқҪ ліөкө¬лҠ” нҳ„мһ¬ н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ. segment-completeк°Җ мҳӨм§Җ м•Ҡмңјл©ҙ WRITING segmentлҠ” finalize лҢҖмғҒмқҙ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.
%% pain point: worker process crash, OOM, host killмІҳлҹј catch/failed handlerк°Җ мӢӨн–үлҗҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ” мһҘм• м—җм„ңлҠ” PROCESSING -> WRITE_DONE resetмқҙ лҲ„лқҪлҗ  мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ.
%% нҳ„мһ¬ лӢЁкі„м—җм„ңлҠ” stale PROCESSING ліөкө¬лҘј кө¬нҳ„н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ. н•„мҡ”н•ҙм§Җл©ҙ reconcile лҳҗлҠ” processing lease кё°л°ҳ ліөкө¬лҘј м¶”к°Җн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.
%% worker processingмқҳ мғҒм„ё кө¬нҳ„ мғҒнғңмҷҖ VLM semantic metadata нҷ•мһҘ м§Җм җмқҖ .mermaid/RTMP/5.video-processing.mmdм—җм„ң лӢӨлЈ¬лӢӨ.
